<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fy nʿmẗ ạlậb ạlgẖny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fī niʿ̊maẗi ạlậbi ạl̊gẖanī̃̊
 naf̊takẖiru wanas̊tarīḥ̊
 fālậna lạ daẙnūnaẗa
 ʿalay̱ ạlãdẖīna fī ạl̊masīḥ̊

[V2]
 2- fakāna ʿad̊lạaⁿ ạản̊ nudān̊
 wāi̹nãmā ạlạib̊nu ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 qad̊ ḥamala ạl̊kẖaṭīãẗa
 bimaẘtihi ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V3]
 3- ại̹n̊sānunā ạl̊ʿatīqu qad̊
 ṣuliba maʿ̊hu wān̊qaḍay̱
 fafīhi qad̊ mut̊nā ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 ḥuk̊maⁿạ wasẖar̊ʿaⁿạ fī ạl̊qaḍā

[V4]
 4- ạảẙḍaⁿạ bihi rūḥu ạl̊ḥayāh̊
 ạảʿ̊taqanā naḥ̊nu ạl̊ʿabīd̊
 kaẙ naḥ̊yā biạl̊qadāsaẗi
 ḥas̊ba maqāminā ạl̊jadīd̊

[V5]
 5- faṭālamā naḥ̊nu hunā
 naṭ̊lubu ʿaẘnaⁿạ wamadad̊
 wālrũwḥu fīnā wabihi
 numītu ạảʿ̊māla ạl̊jasad̊

[V6]
 6- fālrãbũ yaẘmaⁿạ yuq̊bilu
 mina ạlsãmāʾi biạl̊jalạl̊
 ạảẙḍaⁿạ nakūnu mitẖ̊lahu
 wanaḥ̊ẓay̱ bimil̊ʾi ạl̊kamāl̊</lyrics>
<aka>fy nʿmẗ ạlậb ạlgẖny nftkẖr wnstryḥ</aka>
</song>